        public static boolean checkFormat​(List<LinkedHashMap<String,​String>> data,
                                  List<String> expectedHeaders,
                                  List<String> expectedDataFormat)
        Checks the format of data fields parsed from a CSV file against the manually inputted expectedHeaders and expectedDataFormat.
        Parameters:
        data - Data parsed from a CSV file
        expectedHeaders - List of String containing the expected column headers from a CSV file
        expectedDataFormat - List of String containing the expected data format of each field, represented in Regex
        Returns:
        a boolean indicating if all data fields match the expected formats
